
Requirement:

1. npm
2. node
3. aglio

Install:

1. apt-get install npm
2. curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_6.x | sudo -E bash -
3. apt-get install nodejs
4. npm install -g aglio

Usage:

1. make
2. make show (open API document html in firefox)

Reference:

1. https://apiblueprint.org
	- A powerful high-level API description language for APIs.
2. https://github.com/apiaryio/api-blueprint/tree/master/examples
	- api-blueprint examples
3. markdown.tw
	- Markdown example

For ubuntu 15.04 :
If you get the error message in step 2, try to install another version as follow,
"curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_5.x | sudo -E bash -"
